    "We also require the LLM to classify generated Q&A pairs with category labels following the chart-task taxonomy (e.g., data retrieval and find extremum), balancing the distribution of different tasks.",
    "During the generation process, we randomly select some QA pairs for manual checking and ensure they are as accurate as expected.Reasoning process.",
    "Recent studies show that unnecessary step-bystep training annotation leads to downgraded generalizability and instruction-following ability.",
    "For simple questions (e.g., data retrieval of bar charts), the reasoning process does not provide useful information compared to single-word answers.",
    "We only attach reasoning processes to questions that need numerical calculations and visual references."
